cff-version: 1.2.0
title: causal-field
abstract: >
  Gaussian resource-contention fields for multi-agent AI coordination.
  Replaces hard mutex locks with probabilistic interference fields so agents
  sense contention before conflict occurs. Supports adaptive sigma, ASCII
  heatmap rendering, matplotlib visualization, and benchmarking.
  Inspired by 3D Gaussian Splatting (3DGS).
message: "If you use this software, please cite it using these metadata."
